trans-unit.source: Specifies the kind of argument that a <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o tipo de argumento que uma <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"> </xref> representa.

trans-unit.source: The RemoteArgumentKind enumeration is used by the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument.RemoteArgumentKind%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: A enumeração RemoteArgumentKind é usada pelo <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument.RemoteArgumentKind%2A?displayProperty=fullName>propriedade.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument.RemoteArgumentKind%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: An intrinsic data type is a primitive data type (that is, the <xref:System.Type.IsPrimitive%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the type is `true`) or a <xref:System.String>, <xref:System.Decimal>, <xref:System.DateTime>, or <xref:System.DBNull>.
trans-unit.target: Um tipo de dados intrínseco é um tipo de dados primitivo (ou seja, o <xref:System.Type.IsPrimitive%2A?displayProperty=fullName>é de propriedade do tipo `true`) ou um <xref:System.String>, <xref:System.Decimal>, <xref:System.DateTime>, ou <xref:System.DBNull>.</xref:System.DBNull> </xref:System.DateTime> </xref:System.Decimal> </xref:System.String> </xref:System.Type.IsPrimitive%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"></xref> represents an intrinsic data type.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"> </xref> representa um tipo de dados intrínseco.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"></xref> represents an <xref:System.Array> that contains elements of an intrinsic data type.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"> </xref> representa um <xref:System.Array>que contém elementos de um tipo de dados intrínseco.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: This is the default value for the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument.RemoteArgumentKind%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Este é o valor padrão para o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument.RemoteArgumentKind%2A?displayProperty=fullName> propriedade.
